sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor U as User
participant FE as Frontend
participant NC as NotificationController
participant NS as NotificationService
participant DB as NotificationStore
participant SSE as SseEmitterRegistry

U->>FE: Open TaskPilot
FE->>NC: GET /notifications/stream
NC->>SSE: Register emitter by user
SSE-->>FE: SSE connection and heartbeat
Note over NS,DB: A task, comment, or project event occurs
NS->>DB: Save notification
DB-->>NS: notificationId
NS->>SSE: Publish notification event
alt User is online
  SSE-->>FE: event notification.created
  FE-->>U: Update inbox and unread counter
else User is offline
  SSE-->>NS: No active emitter
  NS-->>DB: Notification remains unread
end
